document_data.name: Halls of the Unicorn
document_data.mainbody: The '''Halls of the Unicorn''' was a large temple devoted to [[Mielikki]] in [[Elventree]] around [[1367 DR]].
document_data.Description: The entire temple was set within the hollowed-out trunks of massive fallen trees. The Halls of the Unicorn was the largest temple in Elventree at the time.
document_data.Inhabitants: The temple was run by High Priest [[Chandlar Hummerspoon]] and his five [[druid]] followers.
